                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-04-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 30, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The American schooner <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi>, from Key West, with part
                    of the crew, was captured near San Cayetano, to the westward, while, it is
                    alleged, landing arms for the insurgents, and towed here yesterday. The case
                    subject to marine jurisdiction. I have seen admiral, who tells me it is now
                    under examination of the judge of instruction. I have verbally asked for
                    observance, as heretofore, of the protocol in the trial of the Americans among
                    them, and I shall confirm it in writing.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
